  <p><b><span id="Overview">Objective:</span></b> <span id="md-webpage-description" itemprop="description"><i>Design Coordination</i> aims to coordinate all service design activities, processes and resources. This ITIL process ensures the consistent and effective design of new or changed IT services, service management information systems, architectures, technology, processes, information and metrics.</span></p>
